title: Google\Cloud\Debugger\CloudWorkspaceId
name: CloudWorkspaceId
description: A CloudWorkspaceId is a unique identifier for a cloud workspace. A cloud workspace is a place associated with a repo where modified files can be stored before they are committed.

params.name: name
params.description: The unique name of the workspace within the repo. This is the name chosen by the client in the Source API's CreateWorkspace method.
